ugust von Kotzebue und Ludwig Tieck.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket AV  Literaturwissenschaften 2005-2012z9783110347043oZDB-23-ALW0 cprintz978305005152940uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978305005358540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050053585423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783050053585/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-ALWc2005d2012  aZDB-23-GLCc2000d2014